Package io.github.grumpystuff.grumpyrest_demo.shop

Class Table<T>

java.lang.Object
io.github.grumpystuff.grumpyrest_demo.shop.Table<T>
public final class Table<T> extends Object
Simulates a database table. Note that unlike a relational database, the ID is not part of the row data but stored next to the row -- it is the index in the internal list.
